<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sudden-adj">sudden <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sʌdn/    美 /'sʌdn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>突然的；意外的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a sudden decision / increase 
突然的决定/增长</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a sudden turn in the road 
路上的急转弯</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="all-of-a-sudden">all of a sudden</h3>
<p>1.<strong>突然；冷不防：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They were watching TV when all of a sudden the power went out.
他们正在看电视，突然停电了。</p></div></div>